transcript:
Customer: Hello?
Executive: Bolo.
Customer: Sir, Meenakshi bol rahi hu, kaise ho aap?
Executive: Kaun Meenakshi?
Customer: Sir, aapka jo grand supreme chalta hai na. Yaad aaya sir, ambela wali listing.
Executive: Ha boliye.
Customer: Jo grand supreme IndiaMART pe chalta hai jab aapko ambela ki listing nahi aa rahi thi to aapne approach kiya tha sir. Meenakshi. Sahnawaz ki manager baat kar rahi hu sir. Good evening.
Executive: Boliye good evening.
Customer: Ji. Sir, ek video meeting ka aapne request dala tha aur aap aapse mere Sahnawaz ki connect bhi hui thi, aapki baat bhi hui thi Sahnawaz se.
Executive: Hmm.
Customer: To sir video meeting bhi aapka ho gaya tha Sahnawaz ke sath. Hmm. And sir dusri cheez ye hai ki abhi jaise main aapka catalog review kar rahi thi na. To kuch kuch aisi categories hai. Jisme aapka lead ka consumption kam hai.
Customer: Kya hai?
Executive: Lead ka consumption kam hai sir aapka.
Customer: To kya karna hai?
Executive: Head massager. Sir to us category mein apna lead ka consumption badhaiye jaise ki aapka head massager hai. Healing mats vagera hai, temperature water bottles vagera hai. Ye bahut sari category jo aisi hai jo already usme aa rahi hai.
Customer: Business mein kaise rahega?
Executive: Jisme lead ka consumption aap kam kar rahe hain. Jo high consumption wale hain wo to sahi hai lekin aapki bahut sare product range hai na sir. Main us product range ke liye request kar rahi hu ki aap equally sab pe utna time dijiye use karne ke liye.
Customer: Karna kya hai mujhe kuch samajh mein nahi aa raha aap kya bata rahe ho. 
Executive: Sir aap jaise matlab sir aapki aap kaise bylead consume karte ho? Aapki category hai sir massager wali?
Customer: Ha hai na.
Executive: To uski bylead aap nahi consume kar rahe ho isme aapko kaise nahi samajh mein aa raha sir?
Customer: Samajh mein nahi aa raha.
Executive: Sir kam hai. Kam hai category mein aap karte hain but kam hai to main yahi puchna chah rahi hu kya aap abhi apna isme nahi dekh rahe hain. Jyada lead ki requirement isme nahi hai?
Customer: Sir?
Executive: Ha boliye.
Executive: Sir isme aapka lead ka jo requirement hai wo kam hai kya?
Customer: Nahi kam nahi hai.
Executive: Kam nahi hai na to thik hai isko bhi thoda purchase kijiye, thik hai. Aur aapki kuch category to aisi hai jisme aap bilkul bhi nahi kar rahe ho wo bhi main bata de rahi hu aapko.

Executive: Jaise ki jewelry box hai na. Cosmetic brush set vagera jo aata hai. Usme bahut kam hai sir aapka.
Customer: Ha to karta hu na abhi sahi se chalu kar deta hu usko.
Executive: Ha twist mop mop jo hai aur stainless steel scissors vagera jo hai aur sunflower ka kuch hai aapka. Aur egg boxes jo hai ye sab mein aapka bilkul bhi nahi hai zero hai bylead entire. WhatsApp kar do na kaunsa kaunsa bata raha hu. Aapka bilkul bhi nahi hai. Ha?
Customer: WhatsApp kar do na kaunsa kaunsa hamara hai.
Executive: Main aapko abhi call ke baad na sari details WhatsApp pe share kar rahi hu ki kisme aap sabse jyada kar rahe ho, kisme aap kam kar rahe ho aur kisme aapka zero hai. To ye teen teeno details main aapko bhej rahi hu. Agar aapka dekhiye sir agar kisi mein aapki priority hai that's fine koi dikkat nahi hai lekin parallel agar aapki itni wide range of category ke sath aap registered ho to main aapse request karungi ki aap sare us pe apna wo dijiye time dijiye, thik hai. Equally aap sabke usme kariye kyunki aapke pass bahut sare category to aapke pass scope of business jyada rahega. Thik hai?
Customer: Hmm.
Executive: Ye cheez aur sir dusri cheez ye hai ki aapka na TrustSeal ka renewal hai. Hmm. Thik hai. Aapka wo renewal jo hai aapne last year jo karwaya tha wo Jan mein karwaya tha hamare sath. Hmm. Aapne to humne correction karke aapki jo services live kari thi wo Feb mein kari thi aapki. To abhi kya hai aapka jo aapka chal raha hai na uski price jo hai revised hai. Hmm. Thik hai. Agar aap karoge to main aapko old price ke rate pe aapko kar paungi offer.
Customer: Nahi nahi abhi nahi karna hai kuch nahi karna hai.
Executive: Abhi nahi to sir kab usi samay jab due hoga?
Customer: Karwana hi nahi hai.
Executive: Sir TrustSeal aapne liya aur ab aap keh rahe ho ki aapko karwana hi nahi hai sir. Abhi nahi karna hai isme nahi karna hai.
Executive: To sir kis fir aap kaun se package mein jaoge?
Customer: Dusra hai. Trade India mein jane wale.
Executive: Trade India ka sir business model alag hai sir aap mujhe ye bataiye aapki do do profile IndiaMART pe registered hai kahin to aapko value add hai tabhi to aapne yaha pe register on kiya hai sir na.
Customer: Koi isme nahi karna abhi karna hai kaam hi nahi karna hai.
Executive: Main abhi ki baat nahi kar rahi hu sir main aapko inform kar rahi hu sir aap IndiaMART pe aapko baad mein bhi nahi karna hai.
Executive: To sir aap IndiaMART pe acche khase active hai main wahi puchna chah rahi hu ki kyun nahi karna hai. Agar abhi nahi karna to baad mein bhi kyun nahi karna sir. Response nahi hai iska response nahi hai sir.
Executive: Sir aap kaun se us pe baat kar rahe hai sir ki response nahi hai sir. Abhi dekho na beech mein to naam bhi nahi dikha raha tha tab aapne nahi bataya to wo do mahine pehle se bata raha hu. Sir maine aapko bataya tha na jab aapne apni location Surat ko hi negative mark kar rakha tha sir to hum hi ne bataya na sir aapko. Har ek category ka maine search karke aapko bataya. Paanch account mein paanch account mein sab mein aise hi hai isme. Sir dekhiye main aapko ye nahi keh rahi hu ki abhi aapne phone kiya hai maine phone kiya aap abhi kar do sir main ye nahi keh rahi hu main aapse ye keh rahi hu ki sir price revised hoga. Aap already mere existing customer hai aapne kya diya hai aapko acche se pata hai aap ek saal use karne wale January tak aapka ek saal ho jayega use karne to main aapko ye sari cheeze confirm kar rahi hu sir.
Customer: To main bata raha hu mujhe karna hi nahi hai aisa to bata raha hu.
Executive: Thik hai sir aap na jitni services hum aapko de rahe hain aap please wo category ki details main Sahnawaz se share karwa rahi hu aapke WhatsApp pe please use kijiye sir. Thik hai. 
Customer: Okay thank you.
Executive: Thank you sir.
summary:

- Executive explained TrustSeal benefits and price revision.
